h1. cf-update-instances

h2. Purpose

Scale up or down the number of instances.

h2. Description

Increases or decreases the number of allocated instances of the application.

Usage:
{code:java}
grails cf-update-instances <number> [--appname]
{code}

Required arguments:

* @number@ - The new number of instances

Optional arguments:

* @appname@ - The name of the application
